<comment_formatting_rule>

- Use section comments with dashes for visual separation:
  ```go
  // -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  // Section Name
  // -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  ```
</comment_formatting_rule>

<example type="bad_practice">
## Bad
// -----
// Section Name
// -----
</example>

<example type="good_practice">
## Good
// -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Section Name
// -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
</example>
